Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
write_design_stack_config(25.10)              write_design_stack_config(25.10)

Name
       write_design_stack_config

Syntax
       write_design_stack_config

       [-help]

       {[-xml   <StackedDieFileName>]   [-power_config_file  <PowerConnection-
       File>]}

       Saves the xml file and power config file in the specified path.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information  for each write_design_stack_config parameter. For a
              detailed description of the command and all of  its  parameters,
              use the man command:

              man write_design_stack_config

       -power_config_file <PowerConnectionFile>
              Specifies the file name of the power connection.

       -xml <StackedDieFileName>
              Specifies the file name of the stacked die.

Related Information
              * read_design_stack_config

